        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Avalúo",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。所以起点是[Infra_EtcdCluster]，终点是[Infra_RedisCache]。中间的状态流转能具体说一下吗？比如评估任务创建之后的第一步是什么？",
